N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4222.2 - Change of jockey

State Regulations

Any subsequent change of jockey must be sanctioned by the
judges who, if no satisfactory reason is given for the change may suspend any
person they may think culpable in the matter. Notes
